@iSazonov The `[breaking-change]` tag should be added to the body of the commit message instead of the title of it. Sorry that I didn't point out that specifically.

When squash-merging a breaking change PR in future, please do like the following:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/127450/36620586-a6379adc-18a8-11e8-9432-0fad261ed3d8.png)
